description:
$35 per person | registration required | Shuttle available from Chace Center, 20 North Main Street


Start the day with a beautiful and educational coastal walk led by Nature Lab Biological Programs Designer Jennifer Bissonnette and sustainable fisheries expert Kate Masury. The nature program will be followed by lunch at 12:30. Shuttle departs the Chace Center on North Main Street at 10:15 am.
name: Eating with the Ecosystem
subtitle: Lunch at Tillinghast
